ading resumes word for word.","Ask trusted friends and colleagues to review your finished resume; ask for detailed feedback."],"type":"ul"},"id":"b100254a-a11e-4c7c-a838-cdcef0ab17c9","type":"list"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["Those who review resumes will notice instantly if you have customized your resume to fit their specific needs. Customized resumes are more relevant to the job, more attractive to management and generally get more attention than generic resumes.","So make reviewing your resume easy on the Human Resources department; make it perfectly clear in your resume that you know exactly what the employer wants and that you&#39;ve got it."]},"id":"ce24fb48-3e81-4814-bab1-86b20fd25985","type":"text"}]],"body":null,"legacyId":"article_page_320","url":"/simple-steps-to-customize-your-resume","authors":[{"email":"","slug":"joanne-c-weaver","url":"/author/joanne-c-weaver","dateCreated":"2019-04-17T20:46:58Z","name":"Joanne C. Weaver","dateModified":"2019-04-17T20:46:58Z","id":"pdqScXpqTNqwhpYmpcYG8D","dateImported":null,"site":"toptenreviews"}],"territories":["US","GB"],"companies":[],"dateCreated":"1970-01-01T00:00:00Z","datePublished":"2017-05-16T20:24:59Z","name":"Simple Steps to Customize Your Resume","synopsis":"So you've put together the perfect resume. Now you're ready to send it out to a million employers simultaneously, right? Wrong.","review":{},"strapline":"So you've put together the perfect resume. Now you're ready to send it out to a million employers simultaneously, right? Wrong.","language":"en","dateModified":"1970-01-01T00:00:00Z","id":"LgQDeSkGvAdgWUXdsg6JiW","meta":{"title":"Simple Steps to Customize Your Resume","description":" So you've put together the perfect resume. Now you're ready to send it out to a million employers simultaneously, right? Wrong. Unless your talents are extremely rare, potential employers won't be"},"products":[],"dateImported":"2019-04-17T21:14:05Z","type":"feature","template":"standard","social":{"twitter":{"image":{"st